<p>We have recently seen some <a href="https://thezvi.substack.com/p/ai-1-sydney-and-bing" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">incredible</a> “rogue AI behavior” in Microsoft’s Bing.</p>



